		<title>Senangnya, Kartini ternyata setuju sama saya&#8230;</title>
		<link>http://blog.ardhanareshwari.com/2011/05/bunda-2/</link>
		<comments>http://blog.ardhanareshwari.com/2011/05/bunda-2/#comments</comments>
